title: Spider-Man - Hunt For The Amulet
body:
Tony sends Peter on a mission to Rio De Janeiro to find and recruit a girl named Ava Ayala. But when he gets there, a lot of trouble happens when a power-hungry hunter is after her as well. Follows the MCU Timeline. Takes place a month after The Clash of The Avengers.

New Mission

(Peter’s POV)“Ned…Ned, you there buddy?"I say lightly patting my friend on the cheek."I had a crazy dream,” he groaned,“ We were at your house and Tony Stark was there.” He must’ve been so shocked…

summary: The Avengers as Things My Friends Have Said pt.7
title: The Avengers as Things My Friends Have Said pt.7
body:
Bucky, looking at Thor's burning red eyes: What the hell happened?
Thor: I was in the shower and I had put my hair treatment in as I was scrubbing my body, I felt my hair drying up and I thought "ew," so I dunked my head under the water, totally forgetting that there was treatment in my hair and I opened my eyes.
Bruce, overhearing the conversation: Once I washed my hair with face wash and my face with shampoo.
Bruce: I only realised when I got out.
Scott: Once I washed my hair with conditioner for a whole week because I didn't know the difference between shampoo and conditioning. 
Bucky replying to Scott: I do that now.
